OL,3,CArrest made three years after man's
OL,4,Cdisappearance
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in connection
OL,7,Fwith a three-year-long missing persons
OL,8,Fcase.
OL,10,FRicky Harris, from Aberdare, was 31
OL,11,Fyears old at the time of his
OL,12,Fdisappearance on Saturday, November
OL,13,F18, 2023.
OL,15,FA 41-year-old man from Mountain Ash
OL,16,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Fpreventing a lawful burial and
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice in
OL,19,Fconnection with Ricky's disappearance.
OL,20,FHe remains in police custody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
