OL,3,CArrest made three years after man's
OL,4,Cdisappearance
OL,6,FRicky was last seen on CCTV at around
OL,7,F2.20pm on November 18, 2023, in Maes-Y-
OL,8,FDeri, Aberdare.
OL,10,FHis family previously told ITV Wales
OL,11,Fthey feared the worst had happened. In
OL,12,F2023, Ricky's mum, Alison, said:
OL,13,F"Something in my stomach is telling me
OL,14,Fhe's dead."
OL,16,FSouth Wales Police confirmed on
OL,17,FFriday, June 12, that their
OL,18,Finvestigation into Ricky's
OL,19,Fdisappearance has been exhaustive,
OL,20,Fwith officers continually reviewing
OL,21,Fnew information.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
