OL,3,CArrest made three years after man's
OL,4,Cdisappearance
OL,6,FOfficers are currently searching The
OL,7,FPhurnacite Site in Abercwmboi, a
OL,8,Fprocess that is expected to "take some
OL,9,Ftime to complete.
OL,11,FAnyone with information, or who may
OL,12,Fhave spoken to Ricky in the days or
OL,13,Fweeks leading up to his disappearance,
OL,14,Fis urged to contact South Wales Police.
